artifacts.name: devtools.jar
artifacts.description: Developer tools plugin to show info inside the game.

artifacts.name: socketping.jar
artifacts.description: Ping tiles, npcs, objects and players in game to other people in the socket.

artifacts.name: menuentryswapper.jar
artifacts.description: Set your own entry swaps and/or removal of entries.

artifacts.name: neverlog.jar
artifacts.description: Note: fakes input. Sends a backspace or space key press to the client once every while so you will never log out.

artifacts.name: servervariance.jar
artifacts.description: Shows the time in milliseconds in between game ticks as received from the server.

artifacts.name: specbar.jar
artifacts.description: Spec bar for all weapons under the weapons tab.

artifacts.name: vengeancetracker.jar
artifacts.description: Vengeance tracker shows little vengeance icon on players for which the client knows of they're vengeanced. It only works if the other player is within vision.

artifacts.name: blackjack.jar
artifacts.description: Automatic menu swaps for Menaphites in the desert. This plugin will only work if BL is up-to-date.

artifacts.name: tobadditions.jar
artifacts.description: Tob additions made by losing ticks fixed by me.
